  "http://schema.org/description": "A generalist framework for multi-dimensional automatic spot detection and quantification.SpotMAX is designed to accomplish two tasks:Detecting and quantifying globular-like structures (a.k.a. \"spots\")Segmenting and quantifying fluorescently labelled structuresIt supports 2D, 3D, 4D, and 5D data, i.e., z-stacks, timelapse, and multiple fluorescence channels (and combinations thereof).",
